## Basic questions
[isPiano]?{Is your troubled instrument a piano? [Yes|No] (piano forte falls under the piano cattegory)}

########## Inferable atoms ##########
[isNotPiano]!{The system is made for piano problems only. Fixit can not help you.|}
[isaPiano]!{Then fixit can help you.}

########## Conditional statements ##########
if(not [isPiano]) then [isNotPiano] end
if [isPiano] then [isaPiano] end
